Description of files in TNT-'doc' directory
-------------------------------------------

tnt.doc			Documentation of TNT V1.0 in plain Ascii
tntdoc.html		Documentation of TNT V1.0 in HTML
tntdoc.texinfo		Source for documentation of TNT V1.0

ax25krnl.doc            Release notes for TNT with AX25-kernel interface

COPYING			The GNU general public license

CHANGES			Changes since TNT V1.0

tnt.doc.francais	Documentation of TNT in french language, plain Ascii
			(this is a translation of the TNT V0.9l documentation
			and does not contain a description of the new
			features of TNT V1.0)

iface.doc               Documentation of the interface protocol used on
			the UNIX-socket between TNT and DPBox

Additional information:
-----------------------
To be able to get the documentation of TNT in printable form, in HTML and in
plain Ascii without the need of maintaining several files, I have changed to
'texinfo' format.

To get the documentation in printable form, you must have installed the
TeX-package. Then a 'tex tntdoc.texinfo' will convert the documentation to
'dvi'-format. This format can be printed or displayed directly (eps, xdvi)
or can be converted to postscript format using 'dvips'.
